--@InstallationUtilityFloppyPart1.cm-- modified from MakeLispFloppies.cm-- last edited  27-Jun-83 22:03:14 by Masinter-- last edited by JFung.pasa   13-Sep-84 14:32:21 for Harmony release--filed at [Rose]<Lisp>Harmony>Installation>InstallationUtilityFloppyPart1.cm--  Command file to build Interlisp-D's "Installation Utility" floppy--  to run this command file, type @InstallationUtilityFloppyPart1 <CR> on your exec window from Tajo or Copilot volume-- You need approximately 700 pages to contain all the filesftp Rose directory/c Apilot>11.0>PilotTools>Public retrieve/a<> MakeDLionBootFloppyTool.bcd ftp Rose directory/c <Apilot>11.0>DLionMicrocode>Public> retrieve/a<> FloppyInitial.db Mesa.db ftp Rose directory/c <Apilot>11.0>DLionDiagMicrocode>Public retrieve/a<> MoonBoot.dbftp Rose directory/c <Apilot>11.0>Pilot>Public> retrieve/a<> DLion.germ--following file is protected, check with L. Masinter.pa or JFung.pasa for accessftp Sun directory/c AServices>8.0>Top>Public retrieve/a<> PrometheusDLion.bootftp Rose directory/c <Lisp>Harmony>Installation ret/A<> lisp11SAx000Initial.db ftp Rose directory/c <Lisp>Harmony>Installation ret/A<> SystemTools.bcdftp Rose directory/c <Lisp>Harmony>Installation ret/A<> prometheus.script LispInstallation.bcd  MakeDLionBootFloppyTool.bcd-- Insert new floppy-- Make the following settings in MakeDLionBootFloppyTool:--  Drive: 0--  Floppy Name: Installation Utility--  Initial uCode: FloppyInitial.db--  Diagnostic uCode: MoonBoot.db	--  Pilot uCode: Mesa.db	--  Germ File: DLion.germ	--  Boot File: PrometheusDLion.boot  -- Bug the "Format And Install Boot Files!" command